The vulnerable mechanics are clear now. I’m switching the verifier to a single USDC-backed Uniswap V2 flashswap that funds realistic dust deposits into the USDC-compatible Yearn, Yearn-CRV, Aave, and bare-token paths in the original order, with low-level fallbacks so a failed branch doesn’t kill the attempt.
